        "gg2Qn3hJVgP_text": "<p>Proven Overnight Results</p>",
        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p>I absolutely love that <strong>refreshing</strong>, <strong>cooling feeling </strong>from a skincare product—it’s one of my favorite parts of my routine. Our mask gives you that <strong>calming, spa-like effect</strong>, even when you're just relaxing at home. It soothes, hydrates, and leaves your skin with a gorgeous, radiant glow—such a simple, <strong>luxurious way</strong> to unwind and take care of yourself! If you haven’t tried it yet, you're in for a treat!</p>",
        "gg5jhvAeOg-_text": "<p>Our Lowest Price of the Year</p>",
        "gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-7f8bd3a0-6256-4f60-8956-dcc70f0540a9.jpg",
