        "gg7_objrOEc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-71051f67-8e75-4fa8-b548-3d16cd73cd7a.png",
        "gg8Tjx0drcK_label": "<p>SHOP NOW</p>",
        "gg8qbjp2nD2_text": "<p>Gentle on Sensitive Skin</p>",
        "gg9IIKcaXL6_label": "<p>SHOP NOW</p>",
        "ggFYCvYdkkz_text": "Don't Wait! The Skin You Deserve is on Sale This Summer Sale 💕 💕&nbsp;",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. Celebrity-Favorite",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-46ddba81-6c7e-441b-b2d1-edeebc781354.jpg",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png",
        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p>GUARANTEED: In just a couple of hours, the Nifora facial mask makes your skin glow so brightly you won’t believe your mirror. If you think you've surpassed Korean beauty standards with just one application, you’re right. This is what Nifora can do for you every time you use it.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Molly Richards<br>Last Updated October, 24 2025</p>",
        "ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/For_LP_9.png",
        "ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/Ads_56.png",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. Scientifically Proven Ingredients",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p>Here’s the exciting part—you’re in luck! Our <strong>Summer Sale is on with up to 75% OFF</strong> just for you. We're sure you’ll love the Bio-Collagen Mask, but if not, you will get a refund, no questions asked. It is <strong>60-day risk free</strong>, so why not give it a try? You deserve glowing skin!</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6.&nbsp;Cooling &amp; Soothing Effect",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p>When I hear a product is a <strong>celebrity favorite</strong>, I have to try it—and once I tried our mask, I totally got why it’s so loved. It’s not just about the natural ingredients, but the <strong>amazing results</strong>. People are obsessed with how it gives them that <strong>flawless</strong>, <strong>youthful glow</strong>, and the best part? It’s all natural! If it’s good enough for them, it’s definitely good enough for us!</p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. Sensitive Skin Friendly",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. Our Biggest Summer Sale is LIVE!",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>Shop Now</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "Discover why 40,000+ women switched from trendy beauty products to our affordable Collagen Gel Mask for Youthful and Glowing Skin",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p><strong>As we get older</strong>, our skin definitely needs <strong>more love</strong>. I’ve noticed my skin craves extra hydration to <strong>stay plump and glowing</strong>, and that’s where collagen comes in. Especially in its low-molecular-weight form (sounds fancy, but it works wonders!), it goes deep into your skin to <strong>keep it hydrated and refreshed all day</strong>. Trust me, it keeps my skin looking dewy and healthy, even after a long day!</p>",
        "ggWfV7zqZ5__text": "<p>And a 60-Day, Totally Risk-Free Guarantee</p>",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
